column6: LOGAN DIES PART 2 While Logan remains in a comatose state after his battle with Shogun, Dr. Strange must delve deep into the mystical realms to retrieve his soul. A new and frightful enemy is revealed!
column8: | penciller:Howard Chaykin | colorist:Edgar Delgado | writer:Marc Guggenheim | letterer:Cory Petit | penciller (cover):Arthur Suydam
